t.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>getUint32()</code></strong> メソッドは、符号なし32ビット整数 (unsigned long) 値を <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/DataView\"><code>DataView</code></a> の指定されたバイト単位のオフセットの位置から読み取ります。</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/dataview-getuint32.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>dataview</var>.getUint32(<var>byteOffset</var> [, <var>littleEndian</var>])</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"byteoffset\"><code><var>byteOffset</var></code></dt>\n <dd>ビューの先頭からのバイト単位のオフセットで、データを読み取る位置です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"littleendian\"><code><var>littleEndian</var></code></dt>\n <dd><span class=\"badge inline optional\">省略可</span> 32ビット整数が<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Endianness\">リトルエンディアンとビッグエンディアン</a>のどちらの形式で格納されているかを表します。 <code>false</code> または <code>undefined</code> の場合、ビッグエンディアン値を読み取ります。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>符号なし32ビット整数。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"errors_thrown","title":"発生するエラー","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"rangeerror\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RangeError\"><code>RangeError</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code>byteOffset</code> がビューの末尾を超えて読み取るように設定されている場合に発生します。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"解説","isH3":false,"content":"<p>アライメントの強制はありません。複数バイトの値はどのオフセットからも読み取ることができます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"using_the_getuint32_method","title":"getUint32 メソッドの使用","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> buffer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ArrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> dataview <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">DataView</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>buffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ndataview<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getUint32</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 0</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-dataview.prototype.getuint32\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"ja\">DataView.prototype.getUint32 の定義</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.DataView.getUint32","dataURL":"/ja